<p class="ayah 29-9" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنُدْخِلَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We will surely admit them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the righteous.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/29:9" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3349"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>9<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
