<p class="ayah 29-32" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لُوطًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Lut."</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَحْنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">know better</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنُنَجِّيَنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We will surely save him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَهْلَهُۥٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his family,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWor