<p class="ayah 29-33" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَمَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[that]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُسُلُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our messengers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لُوطًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) Lut</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سِىٓءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he was distressed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَضَاقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and felt straitened</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَرْعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(and) uneasy.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"(Do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَخَفْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">fear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْزَنْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">grieve.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, we</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُنَجُّوكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) save you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَهْلَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and your family,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱمْرَأَتَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your wife.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">She</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْغَـٰبِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who remain behind.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/29:33" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3373"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>33<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 29-34" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, we</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُنزِلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) bring down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَهْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذِهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَرْيَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">town</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رِجْزًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) sky,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">because</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they have been</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْسُقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">defiantly disobedient."</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/29:34" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3374"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>34<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 29-35" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَد</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And verily,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَّرَكْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have left</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَةَۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a sign,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيِّنَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) evidence</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّقَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْقِلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who use reason.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/29:35" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3375"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>35<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
