<p class="ayah 29-38" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَادًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Aad</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَثَمُودَاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and Thamud,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَد</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and verily,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَّبَيَّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(has) become clear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّسَـٰكِنِهِمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their dwellings.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَزَيَّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And made fair-seeming</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّيْطَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Shaitaan</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْمَـٰلَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their deeds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَصَدَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and averted